{"tid":2294601,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"四寶三陽買Sony相機保養問題","createTime":"2020-11-21T06:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T00:36:14.000Z","uid":1011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b5408e92e65536e8bf5fd798769a169ff16d7edd","tid":2294601,"uid":1011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:52:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人係呢兩間鋪買過sony相機而保養期內需要維修？ 有既話sony受唔受，見兩間鋪都唔係特約零售商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f7fe5112a933586a3235b88ad09fe1965e6174","tid":2294601,"uid":293472,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#123 老夫要上了&bull;10 個月前<br />\n三陽又好，四寶又好都唔會幫襯，<a href=\"http://price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprice.com&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=f9fdcf4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">price.com</a>個堆鋪，就算係行貨都係拆貨來(official dearies ，例如和井，蘇靈，數碼城再拆比佢哋。)<br />\n<br />\n有問題拎返廠維修唔會睇佢哋啲單，可能被廠房reject得多，呢家會再比多一張official dearies單你，但唔知係咪每個人都比。官方原廠有其他嘢送，例如電池和認憶咭，或者coupon，佢哋未必會有，有都收埋再賣返出去。<br />\n<br />\n講咗咁多，<a href=\"http://price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprice.com&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=f9fdcf4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">price.com</a>真係當睇參考價算，買唔買得過，消費者要自行承擔風險。<br />\n<br />\n［黑店］ 三陽數碼<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/noweotX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/noweotX</a>"},{"pid":"557d564b0eceefa97300fce13ccc5b9837b90c97","tid":2294601,"uid":12443,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:23:28.000Z","msg":"唔係想推薦，但平心而論，我買過幾次，完全無問題，不過你唔好乜都唔識就上去買，揀好哂，格哂價先囉<br />\n同埋sony嗰度我登記過3件係四bo買既都無問題，係咪唔關事？"},{"pid":"a2f042aefad5362587595d5dd09f023ba578534f","tid":22946